summary: 1993  was a common year starting on Friday of the Gregorian calendar.
full_text: 1993  was a common year starting on Friday  of the Gregorian calendar, the 1993rd year of the Common Era  and Anno Domini  designations, the 993rd year of the 2nd millennium, the 93rd year of the 20th century, and the 4th year of the 1990s decade.
